description: Turns raw customer tickets into engineering-ready bug reports — with reproduction steps, customer impact, ARR at risk, and linked tickets — so engineers get context, not noise. Keep Zendesk, Jira, and Linear. Replace the Slack pings, the half-formed Jira tickets, and the support-to-engineering translation tax.
